  "title": "삼성어린이박물관",
  "addDate": "2011. 12. 14.",
  "categoryNo": "42",
  "parentCategoryNo": "1",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=110126438224",
  "html_size": 185113,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110126438224\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110126438224\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \r\n<p>엄마가 공부하러 외출해서 </p>\r\n<p>제가 첫째 아들을 혼자서 담당해야 하는 일요일. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>뭘 할까 하다 삼성어린이 박물관을 가보자! 하고는 출발.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>아무런 정보도 없이 ^^</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>애들 박물관에는 뭐가 있을까.. 궁금해 하면서 갔죠</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>입장하면 먹을 파는 곳이 없다길래 우선 식사먼저.. </p>\r\n<p>쌀국수 ^^</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/52ea90c92dc2b5b3.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"736\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 550px; rheight: 736px\" id=\"20111214_81/isuhani_13238268300385aR0s_JPEG/IMG_1908.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A40C1750')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/52ea90c92dc2b5b3.jpg\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>너무 배부르면 안되니까 적당히 먹고 드디어 입장. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/65d94261c52f9d1d.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"736\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 550px; rheight: 736px\" id=\"20111214_157/isuhani_1323826918698B4NBf_JPEG/IMG_1913.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A40C1750')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/65d94261c52f9d1d.jpg\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></p>\r\n<p>올라가면서 찍은 입구 및 로비... </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" />&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/1070113e2ed2c499.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"736\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 550px; rheight: 736px\" id=\"20111214_114/isuhani_1323826919166fFmkK_JPEG/IMG_1914.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A40C1750')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/1070113e2ed2c499.jpg\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>올라가는 계단. </p>\r\n<p>1층은 로비이고, 2,3,4 층이 박물관. </p>\r\n<p>각 층마다 주제가 있던데..</p>\r\n<p>기억 안나요.. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/197b9eea53979a3e.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"736\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 550px; rheight: 736px\" id=\"20111214_109/isuhani_13238270728771MHhh_JPEG/IMG_1916.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A40C1750')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/197b9eea53979a3e.jpg\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></p>\r\n<p>빛과 사진? 이란 주제의 방.. </p>\r\n<p>카메라도 있고, 여러가지 영상을 활용한 작품들이 전시. 애들이 가지고 놀 수도 있는 것들.</p>\r\n<p>아~ 어린이 박물관이 이런 것들을 전시하는구나.... 라고 생각하고 다음 방으로 이동. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/9fc7ae6a223c169d.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"736\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 550px; rheight: 736px\" id=\"20111214_287/isuhani_1323827073282tWdJR_JPEG/IMG_1918.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A40C1750')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/9fc7ae6a223c169d.jpg\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></p>\r\n<p>공사장을 테마로 한 공간. </p>\r\n<p>음..</p>\r\n<p>테마가 있는.</p>\r\n<p>놀이터네?</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4412120c1e94504d.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"736\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 550px; rheight: 736px\" id=\"20111214_167/isuhani_13238270736454Kpsx_JPEG/IMG_1925.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A40C1750')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4412120c1e94504d.jpg\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></p>\r\n<p>물을 활용한 놀이 시설들. </p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/1eea54e0f7d6c5e3.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"736\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 550px; rheight: 736px\" id=\"20111214_199/isuhani_1323827074081rICBU_JPEG/IMG_1922.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A40C1750')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/1eea54e0f7d6c5e3.jpg\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></p>\r\n<p>여기는 주방을 테마로.. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>요리하는 흉내내기를 좋아하는 녀석이라 한참을 노네요.</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4000c59c297540c3.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"410\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 550px; rheight: 410px\" id=\"20111214_174/isuhani_13238270745935zdjC_JPEG/IMG_1933.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A40C1750')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4000c59c297540c3.jpg\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></p>\r\n<p>의무실 앞에 세워져있는 모형 구급차.</p>\r\n<p>남자애라서인지 역시 차를 좋아해요..</p>\r\n<p>안내리겠다는걸 억지로 내렸네요</p>\r\n<p>타려고 기다리는 친구들이 많아서요</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/954e9e27a9304569.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"736\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 550px; rheight: 736px\" id=\"20111214_85/isuhani_1323827075033SXtNN_JPEG/IMG_1948.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A40C1750')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/954e9e27a9304569.jpg\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></p>\r\n<p>역시나 자동차!!! ㅎㅎ</p>\r\n<p>그 중에 경찰차!!! </p>\r\n<p>이 날 하루 중 가장 재밌었다고 본인이 말하더군요. 경찰차</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ce288db8517d70b2.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"736\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 550px; rheight: 736px\" id=\"20111214_37/isuhani_1323827075457yb2EF_JPEG/IMG_1949.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A40C1750')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ce288db8517d70b2.jpg\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>소꿉놀이 할 수 있는 공간에서</p>\r\n<p>'아빠 배고프다, 가자'</p>\r\n<p>라고 말하니</p>\r\n<p>'삼물탕이야, 아빠 먹어'</p>\r\n<p>라면서 한그릇 갖다 줍니다. ㅎㅎ</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>----------</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>오후 1시 경에 들어가서.. 4시 반이 되서야 겨우 나올 수 있었네요</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>나와서 국수 먹고 싶다고 해서 점심 먹었던 </p>\r\n<p>국수집에 다시 갔습니다. </p>\r\n<p>반나절 신나게 놀았는지, 말도 잘 듣고 계속 흥얼거리고 좋아라 하네요</p>\r\n<p>그렇게 배불리 먹고는</p>\r\n<p>차에 타자마자 골아떨어지네요.. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>삼성어린이 박물관은 각종 놀이시설의 집합소 같네요 ^^ </p>\r\n<p>키즈카페 보다 가격은 저렴하고 (대신 음료 제공은 없고, 내부에도 먹을게 없어요)</p>\r\n<p>다양하게 놀거리들이 있네요. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
